This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-ntp layer.

This layer is for NTP on the stm32mp1 hardware.  Currently only adds the pps-gpio module to the kernel.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/STMicroelectronics/meta-st-stm32mp
  branch: thud

See https://wiki.st.com/stm32mpu/index.php/STM32MP1_Distribution_Package

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-ntp layer to your build


I. Adding the meta-ntp layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-ntp'
